page.title: 18Families - Naomi
page.content: My name is Naomi Warren and I am 8 years old and I have a grown up sister called Mandy who is 23 and has a baby called Jodie. I ahave a brother called Vince who is 19. I have a dog and a fish as pets. The dog is called Jake. I like eating, especially chicken and turkey, but I don't like cabbage or carrot, but I have to eat some - Mum says. My favourite books are written by Enid Blyton. I like ghost stories. We have two cars and go in the back of the red one with my dog. We have lots of relations in Hertfordshire and London. My Mum and Dad come from London. My Dad is a builder who works in Stowmarket. My best friend is Carla, who lives on Blackheath.
